STATE of North Carolina
v.
Brandon LEE No. 356P17-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. December 28, 2018 Brandon Lee, for Lee, Brandon. Daniel P. O'Brien, N. Lorrin Freeman, District Attorney, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Defendant on the 27th of December 2018 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 28th of December 2018."
